data.description: Welcome to 17495 E Chenango Dr, Aurora, CO! This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home sits on a generous corner lot, offering ample space and privacy. The main floor boasts an inviting open concept design flooded with natural light, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The kitchen features chic wood counters and trendy green cabinets, giving it a Scandinavian vibe and adding a touch of elegance to the space. The recently updated powder room on the main floor adds modern convenience. Upstairs, you'll find two cozy bedrooms and a full bathroom, complete with a newer stackable washer and dryer for your convenience. The expansive backyard is perfect for outdoor enthusiasts, featuring a large gate for trailer parking and providing endless possibilities for outdoor activities. Plus, there's no HOA, giving you the freedom to personalize and enjoy your property as you wish. As an added bonus, the lucky buyer will have the opportunity to choose the new siding color, receive a brand-new roof, and enjoy a freshly refinished deck. Don't miss out on this fantastic home with incredible potential in a desirable location in the Cherry Creek School District! Showings start next Thursday, February 8th.
